    "description": "<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n\tMasstron is one of the leaders in the supply of Fiber Optic products in Singapore. Masstron was founded in Singapore in 1994 with the vision that Fiber Optics would revolutionize the way people interact, work and play.</p>\r\n<div style=\"zoom: 1; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n\t&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"zoom: 1; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n\tOur Vision is to be Your Ultimate Partner in Total Communication Solutions. We are a One-Stop Total Communication Supplier and Service Provider to serve your demand and needs. We support total solution for Data Communication and Computer Networking industry, Industrial Automation and Process Control Environment, OEM and Contract Manufacturers, Telecommunication, Security, Photonics and Research Institutions.</div>\r\n<div style=\"zoom: 1; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n\t&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"zoom: 1; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n\tWe have various positions available which offer both challenges and rewards. Join us for a fulfilling and rewarding career.</div>\r\n<div style=\"zoom: 1; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n\t<br />\r\n\twww.masstron.com</div>\r\n",
